@startuml

skinparam padding 6

!include ../../../../../../tooling/styles/plantuml/structural/component-diagram-style.iuml

title <b>Software Architecture Viewtypes</b>\nModule views document static code structure

rectangle "**Module Views**\n<i>Static Code Structure</i>\n\nCode units, packages,\nclasses, dependencies,\ninheritance hierarchies" as MV <<module>>

rectangle "**C&C Views**\n<i>Runtime Structure</i>\n\nRunning components,\nconnectors, data flow,\ninteraction protocols" as CC <<cnc>>

rectangle "**Allocation Views**\n<i>Mapping Structure</i>\n\nDeployment, work\nassignment, build &\nrelease processes" as AV <<alloc>>

MV -[#2563EB,bold]right-> CC : " code implements\n components "
MV -[#2563EB,bold]right-> AV : " code maps to\n environments "

note bottom of MV
  <b>Primary concerns:</b>
  Code organization · Development planning
  Impact analysis · Team assignment
end note
@enduml

